Description: Overview
        ========
        
        ``repoze.bfg.layouts`` provides a site layout story for the ``repoze.bfg``
        framework. It uses familiar technologies like CSS3 to dynamically
        inject dynamic content into static HTML.
        
        Consult the documentation for ``chameleon.html`` for information on
        how to write templates.
        
        
